---
---

<section
  id="about"
  style="background-color: #FAF7F4; padding: 0;"
>
  <div
    style="max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 100px 48px; display: flex; gap: 80px; align-items: flex-start;"
    class="about-inner"
  >
    <!-- Left sticky panel -->
    <div
      class="about-sticky"
      style="flex: 0 0 420px; min-height: 560px; border-radius: 4px; position: sticky; top: 100px; overflow: hidden; isolation: isolate;"
    >
      <!-- Real store photo -->
      <img
        src="/images/store-flatlay.jpg"
        alt="Inside Glamour Boutique Enniscorthy"
        loading="lazy"
        style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;display:block;min-height:560px;"
      />
      <!-- Est. overlay -->
      <div style="position:absolute;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;padding:28px 32px;background:linear-gradient(to top,rgba(44,44,44,0.75) 0%,transparent 100%);">
        <p style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:32px;font-weight:300;color:#fff;margin:0;letter-spacing:0.08em;">Est. 1999</p>
        <p style="font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);margin:4px 0 0;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;">26 Main Street, Enniscorthy</p>
      </div>
      <!-- Hidden watermark structure kept for graceful fallback -->
      <div style="display:none;text-align: center; padding: 40px; position: relative;">
        <span
          style="position: absolute; top: 50%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%); font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 120px; font-weight: 300; color: rgba(212,129,154,0.15); white-space: nowrap; user-select: none; pointer-events: none; line-height: 1;"
        >
          Est.
        </span>
        <p
          style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 300; color: #D4819A; margin: 0 0 8px; position: relative; z-index: 1; letter-spacing: 0.1em;"
        >
          Est.
        </p>
        <p
          style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 96px; font-weight: 300; color: #2C2C2C; margin: 0; line-height: 1; position: relative; z-index: 1;"
        >
          1999
        </p>
        <div style="margin-top: 24px; position: relative; z-index: 1;">
          <div style="width: 32px; height: 1px; background-color: #D4819A; margin: 0 auto 16px;"></div>
          <p style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: #9E9085; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; margin: 0;">
            Enniscorthy
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Right scrolling content -->
    <div style="flex: 1; padding-top: 20px;">
      <p
        style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.3em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #9E9085; margin-bottom: 20px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px;"
      >
        <span style="width:28px;height:1px;background-color:#D4819A;display:inline-block;"></span>
        Our Story
      </p>
      <h2
        class="about-heading"
        style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: clamp(36px, 4vw, 56px); font-weight: 300; color: #2C2C2C; line-height: 1.1; margin: 0 0 40px;"
      >
        26 Years of<br />Honest Fashion
      </h2>

      <div class="about-body" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 28px;">
        <p
          class="about-para"
          style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: #2C2C2C; line-height: 1.85; margin: 0; opacity: 0.85;"
        >
          Glamour Boutique has been a cornerstone of Enniscorthy's Main Street since 1999. Founded by Mary Hudson-Ryan, and now home to a team of passionate stylists — Miriam, Lyndsey, Nadia and Jo — we've built our reputation on one simple principle: honest fashion advice.
        </p>

        <p
          class="about-para"
          style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: #2C2C2C; line-height: 1.85; margin: 0; opacity: 0.85;"
        >
          We stock the labels that actually work for real women — Peruzzi, Robell, Deck, Marie Mero, Masai and more — because beautiful clothes should feel as good as they look.
        </p>

        <p
          class="about-para"
          style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: #2C2C2C; line-height: 1.85; margin: 0; opacity: 0.85;"
        >
          New stock arrives every single week. Come in, try everything on, and let us find your perfect fit.
        </p>

        <!-- Team callout -->
        <div style="margin-top: 20px; padding: 32px; background-color: rgba(212,129,154,0.08); border-left: 2px solid #D4819A; border-radius: 0 4px 4px 0;">
          <p style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 20px; font-style: italic; color: #D4819A; margin: 0 0 12px;">
            "We believe every woman deserves to feel wonderful in what she wears."
          </p>
          <p style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; color: #9E9085; margin: 0; letter-spacing: 0.05em;">
            — Mary Hudson-Ryan, Founder
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Meet the team -->
        <div style="margin-top: 16px;">
          <p style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #9E9085; margin-bottom: 16px;">
            The Team
          </p>
          <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 12px;">
            {['Mary', 'Miriam', 'Lyndsey', 'Nadia', 'Jo'].map((name) => (
              <span
                style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 18px; color: #2C2C2C; padding: 8px 20px; border: 1px solid rgba(212,129,154,0.3); border-radius: 24px;"
              >
                {name}
              </span>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-inner {
      flex-direction: column !important;
      gap: 40px !important;
      padding: 60px 24px !important;
    }
    .about-sticky {
      position: relative !important;
      top: auto !important;
      flex: none !important;
      width: 100% !important;
      min-height: 280px !important;
    }
  }
</style>
